title: Managing Partner
headline: Managing Partner at Global Green Food Trading LLC

organization.name: Global Green Foods
organization.raw_address: Plot No. 597-248, Warehouse 2, Dubai Investments Park 2 - Dubai - Émirats arabes unis
organization.seo_description:
Creators & distributors of legendary food products for those on the go. The 
UAE home of King, Azura & Pana Organic products.
organization.short_description:
Global Green Foods was formed in early 2010 with one goal in mind; to bring healthy and organic foods to the people of the UAE. 

- One recent problem with the food industry is it's growing dependency on unhealthy, cheap and genetically modified food stuffs. Although this may have its financial advantages for the large conglomerates, which sell such foods, it is rapidly causing early age obesity, heart-related health problems and an overall decline in fitness levels amongst the nation. 

- Our mission is clear. To show the consumers and the competition alike that tasty, honest, and healthy food can be accessible to all consumers. 

- Everyone is aware, if we want to make the right impact on the industry we have to be realistic. This is why it is our priority to ensure we are affordable compared to the competition. Being a relatively small company, we do not have large overheads or countless shareholders to please, meaning our costs stay low - a fact which can be seen from our prices. This way we are considered a real alternative in the market.

- Naturally, price is only half of the story. What good is a cheap product, which is low in quality and taste?

It is this question that drives our company. We guarantee every product in our range to be nothing less than the best in terms of quality, taste, ingredients and presentation.

organization.name: Tulsidas
organization.raw_address: po box 430 dubai, dubai, dubai, united arab emirates
organization.seo_description: Tulsidas is a Dubai based leading FMCG supplier and distribution company with prominent food and non-food branded products. We source and supply exceptional quality products while providing consistent service. We're proudly a HACCP & ISO22000:2005 certified company.
organization.short_description:
About Tulsidas Lalchand General Trading LLC

🌟 Who We Are

Founded in 1870 and based in Dubai, Tulsidas is an industry-leading food and healthcare company. We've carved our niche by consistently offering exceptional quality products across multiple sectors including retail, hotel supplies, and premium dining establishments.

🍲 Our Food Portfolio

We proudly offer a diverse product range from Continental Instant Coffee and American Tuna to Indra Pure Ghee. We are also the authorized distributors for premium brands like Sirkku Sugar Cubes, La Tourangelle Oils, and Sona Dairy Products.

🍽️ Hospitality & Gourmet Dining

We specialize in hotel, catering, and restaurant supplies, serving establishments all the way up to Michelin-starred restaurants in the UAE. Our 'Chef's Choice' sourcing service ensures that we can provide any specialty product a chef might require.

🌿 Health & Home Care

We go beyond food with our Super Antiseptic Disinfectant and a versatile range of home care products, ensuring a holistic approach to quality and wellness.

🎯 Our Mission

Committed to excellence, we aim to create sustainable, long-term value for our consumers, clients, and communities. We are the go-to source for high-quality, reliable supplies in the hospitality and food sectors.

🛠 Quality & Safety

We're HACCP & ISO22000:2005 certified, underscoring our unwavering commitment to food safety. Our team is rigorously trained to ensure a 100% reliable food safety environment.

🌍 Our Heritage

Tulsidas Lalchand set foot in Dubai in 1870 and saw the untapped potential to serve the local community with essential food commodities. Today, the fifth generation continues to build on his legacy.

📍 Global Footprint

Though our headquarters are in Dubai, we have a significant presence across the Middle East. We not only market major Fast-Moving Consumer Goods (FMCG) but also create and market premium and gourmet brands for a discerning clientele.

Matcha is a high-grade green tea powder, that is packed full of healthy nutrients and antioxidants. This magical powder provides a clean and gentle caffeinated buzz, yet totally eliminating the awful crash and jittering feeling. 

We believe that BLU Matcha can make a positive impact in the caffeinated beverage world and create a contemporary, stylish and funky movement.
